RACE.FOOTNOTES: WHEN IN ROME was away alertly and quickly made the lead, was nicely rated on the front end, led throughout and widened late under firm handling. BUILT LIKE TARZAN was allowed to settle early, swung five wide in the stretch and had a mild bid . COPPER HARBOR raced wide and was no threat. OLD MAN MAC pressed early on the inside and weakened in the lane. ROGERS GINGER tracked three wide and faded in the stretch. GANSITO contended for a half, then gave way in the stretch. PER OHIO STATE RACING COMMISSION RULING #2023-TDN-07, DATED 04/11/2023 WHEN IN ROME WAS DQ'D DUE TO A POSITIVE TEST.

STRAIGHT TO GO was unhurried early, rallied on the inside and improved. FRANCIA (PER) chased the speed and weakened in mid stretch. KILLOEAN ROSE raced wide and was no menace. WINEDOWN was no factor. SAPPHIRE MOONLIGHT had early foot and was through after a half. TEST YOUR FAITH had no speed and trailed. The rider of IRON WILMA claimed foul against the rider of HOPES PETUNIA for alleged interference in late stretch. After viewing the tape the stewards took no action.
